          <text>
                    <body>
                              <div xml:id="d.1">
                                        <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Albert Peregi (Linz, 21
                                                  February 1530)</head>
                                        <floatingText type="regesta">
                                                  <body>
                                                  <p xml:id="reg.p.1"> How distant they have become
                                                  and how much this saddens him, others will tell
                                                  Peregi. If he does not conduct his business more
                                                  wisely, it will not end well.</p>
                                                  </body>
                                        </floatingText>
                                        <pb facs="https://www.eleveltar.hu/kereso-portlet/spring/digitalcontent/getcontent/preservica/8F050FF9-7EF8-401A-85CA-2F6E3EB60DE0
                                                  "/>
                                        <p xml:id="p.1">Ad eundem.</p>
                                        <p xml:id="p.2">Incredibile dictu est, quantum a tuis rebus
                                                  sim alienatus. Non multo post tuum hinc discessum
                                                  varia de te tuisque rebus habuimus nova, quae
                                                  quantam tristitiam mihi attulerint, ex aliorum te
                                                  litteris malo, quam meis cognoscere. Propter
                                                  amicitiam nostram communem tua et tristia et laeta
                                                  sunt mihi communia. Nisi igitur in tempore
                                                  prudenter rebus tuis consulueris, nihil tibi boni
                                                  spero futurum. Vale.</p>
                                        <p xml:id="p.3">Ex <placeName>Lincio</placeName> 21.
                                                  Februarii 1530.</p>
                              </div>
                    </body>
